'''羅倫·布克斯'''（{{lang-en|Lauren Beukes}}，{{bd|1976年|6月5日||}}），是一位[[南非|南非]][[小說家|小說家]]、[[短篇小說|短篇小說]][[作家|作家]]、記者及電視編劇。

== 生平 ==
羅倫·布克斯出生於[[約翰內斯堡|約翰內斯堡]]，目前住在[[開普敦|開普敦]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.firststep.me/index.php/ultimate-careers/career-interviews/367-lauren-beukes-the-writer-who-is-inspired-by-the-world |title=Lauren Beukes the writer who is inspired by the world | FirstStep.me- The Fun Side of Being Serious – Careers, Education, Finance, Travel & Business |publisher=FirstStep.me |date= |accessdate=3 June 2013 |archive-date=2013-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203060803/http://www.firststep.me/index.php/ultimate-careers/career-interviews/367-lauren-beukes-the-writer-who-is-inspired-by-the-world |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她擁有[[開普敦大學|開普敦大學]]創意寫作碩士學位。她曾擔任自由撰稿人十年，包括在[[紐約|紐約]]及[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]的兩年。

她是《[[我會我會回來找妳|我會我會回來找妳]]》（The Shining Girls）作者，這是一本關於[[時間旅行|時間旅行]][[連環殺手|連環殺手]]的小說。[[MRC|MRC]]和[[萊昂納多·迪卡普里奧|萊昂納多·迪卡普里奧]]團隊將小說改編為[[電視劇|電視劇]]<ref name="Hollywood Reporter">{{cite web
| url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/hot-book-shining-girls-acquired-561252
| title = Hot Book Shining Girls Acquired
| work = Hollywood Reporter
| accessdate = 21 July 2013
| archive-date = 2013-06-07
