| dead-url = no
}}</ref>。

2013年4月15日，《[[我會我會回來找妳|我會我會回來找妳]]》由蘭登書屋在南非發行<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.randomstruik.co.za/books/the-shining-girls/5011|title=The Shining Girls – Fiction – Lauren Beukes,  – 9781415202012|accessdate=6 May 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130423165647/http://randomstruik.co.za/books/the-shining-girls/5011|archivedate=2013年4月23日}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.exclus1ves.co.za/books/Shining-Girls-AuthorLauren-Beukes/000000000100000000001000000000000000000000000009781415202012/|title=The Shining Girls|accessdate=6 May 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130227173919/http://www.exclus1ves.co.za/books/Shining-Girls-AuthorLauren-Beukes/000000000100000000001000000000000000000000000009781415202012/|archivedate=2013年2月27日}}</ref>，2013年4月25日，由英國哈珀柯林斯出版社發行，2013年6月4日於美國[[穆赫蘭出版社|穆赫蘭出版社]]發行<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.harpercollins.co.uk/Titles/76669/the-shining-girls-lauren-beukes-9780007464562|title=The Shining Girls : Lauren Beukes – HarperCollins|accessdate=6 May 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130627175053/http://www.harpercollins.co.uk/Titles/76669/the-shining-girls-lauren-beukes-9780007464562|archive-date=2013-06-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[哈珀柯林斯|哈珀柯林斯]]已經贏得國際出版權利<ref>{{Cite web|title=Bidding frantic for Beukes' thriller|url=http://www.thebookseller.com/news/bidding-frantic-beukes-thriller.html|last=Williams|first=Charlotte|date=7 October 2011|publisher=The Bookseller|accessdate=6 May 2013|archive-date=2013-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515204604/http://www.thebookseller.com/news/bidding-frantic-beukes-thriller.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Shining Girl Beukes lands at HC|url=http://www.thebookseller.com/news/shining-girl-beukes-lands-hc.html|last=Williams|first=Charlotte|publisher=The Bookseller|date=21 October 2011|accessdate=6 May 2013|archive-date=2013-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130421075203/http://www.thebookseller.com/news/shining-girl-beuk